qas.question: What period was the first known city states established in Myanmar?

Were any of the early civilizations influenced by each other and if so by what how did it occur?

answers.text: The Pyu culture was heavily influenced by trade with India

qas.question: What Myanmar import from other countries that has been of major importance?

answers.text: Buddhism as well as other cultural, architectural and political concepts
